
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Why is Azure Diagnostics API needed?

* To collect diagnostic data such as performance monitoring, system event logs

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

What is Azure Resource Manager?

* A service provided by Azure to provide management and application deployment in Azure

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

What is NSG?

* Has a list of Access Control rules which either allows/denies network traffic to subnets

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

What is an Availability Set?

* Is a logical grouping of VMs that allows Azure to understand how application is built to provide redundancy and availability
* Too meet the 99.95% Azure SLA

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Why CDN?

* To reduce load time and bandwidth and speed responsiveness

-------------------------------------------------------------------------